T1  - Ex-Day Returns of Stock Distributions: An Anchoring Explanation
AU  - Chang, Eric C.
AU  - Lin, Tse-Chun
AU  - Luo, Yan
AU  - Ren, Jinjuan
Y1  - 2017/10/20
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2019/03/01
