TY  - JOUR
T1  - Risk Aversion and Precautionary Savings in Dynamic Settings
AU  - Bommier, Antoine
AU  - Grand, François Le
Y1  - 2018/04/26
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2019/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2017.2959
